content:
Great laundry timer app designed for laundromat. Also useful at home if you 
just use one of the machine timers. Could also be great if you have 
multiple washers at home... little boys wanted to have a second washer...
Now I know when my laundry is done.
Needs quick buttons for default times. And a setting to choose how many machines you have access to. ( I have 5)
Love it. I need another app  exactly like this one no colorized version.

I live in an apartment building so it helps a lot to have a timer for the shared washer and dryer, especially since they run on different time cycles. Now I can do the wash and dry with great efficiency.  This app is very well designed - easy to use, (intuitive) and simplistic design.  It also has a reference for laundry symbols.  So far it hasn't crashed on me and it seems to work well without interfering with other apps or functions.
This is a great app especially if you live in an apartment....works just like it says and hasn't bugged out
